           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">EPA faults Mississippi state communications on water risks ahead of Jackson crisis</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Mississippi’s state health department did not adequately enforce the Safe Drinking Water Act in Jackson, contributing to the 2022 crisis that left 150,000 residents without drinking water, according to a report released Tuesday by the Environmental Protection Agency’s (EPA) Office of Inspector Gener
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/13/epa-faults-mississippi-state-communications-on-water-risks-ahead-of-jackson-crisis/"  >(Zack Budryk, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
