           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Dolphins' Tyreek Hill confident he could beat Noah Lyles in sprint, takes shot at gold medalist over COVID</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Miami Dolphins star wide receiver Tyreek Hill was confident he could beat American Olympic gold medalist Noah Lyles in a sprint and was critical over his COVID diagnosis.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/13/dolphins-tyreek-hill-confident-he-could-beat-noah-lyles-sprint-takes-shot-gold-medalist-over-covid/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 03:59:01 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 03:59:01 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/08/13/jordan-chiles-medal-inquiry-usa-gymnastics-says-arbitration-panel-wont-reconsider-decision.webp" alt="Jordan Chiles medal inquiry: USA Gymnastics says arbitration panel won't reconsider decision"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Jordan Chiles medal inquiry: USA Gymnastics says arbitration panel won't reconsider decision</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      USA Gymnastics officials say an arbitration panel won't reconsider a decision asking gymnast Jordan Chiles to return the bronze medal she was awarded in the floor exercise at the Paris Olympics. USA Gymnastics says it will continue efforts to let Chiles keep the medal.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/13/jordan-chiles-medal-inquiry-usa-gymnastics-says-arbitration-panel-wont-reconsider-decision/"  >(The Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 21:02:42 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 21:02:42 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
