           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Antonio Brown and Le'Veon Bell joked about, debated what it means to have CTE and whether they have it</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Antonio Brown and Le&apos;Veon Bell debated what they thought the degenerative disease CTE actually was in a podcast episode Monday and questioned whether either of them had it.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/14/antonio-brown-leveon-bell-joked-debated-what-means-have-cte-do-have-it/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
