  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/08/12/get-ready-for-the-2028-summer-olympics-in-oklahoma-city.webp" alt="Get ready for the 2028 Summer Olympics in ... Oklahoma City?"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Get ready for the 2028 Summer Olympics in ... Oklahoma City?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Competitions for softball and the canoe slalom program will be held more than 1,300 miles from the host city in OKC because the Los Angeles area lacks proper facilities, LA28 organizers said.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/12/get-ready-for-the-2028-summer-olympics-in-oklahoma-city/"  >(Billy Gates, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 03:17:57 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 03:17:57 +0000">
