           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Jordan Chiles 'earned that medal': Gymnast Dominique Dawes</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Dominique Dawes explained that even those in the gymnastics world "are very confused by this whole situation.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/13/jordan-chiles-olympics/"  >(Anna Kutz, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
