           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Australian b-girl's father-in-law takes swipe at judges over Olympic breaking score</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Rachael Gunn&apos;s father-in-law defended the Australian Olympian&apos;s breaking performance in Paris and took a swipe at the judges over the putrid score.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/13/australian-b-girls-father-in-law-takes-swipe-judges-over-olympic-breaking-score/"  >(Fox News)</a>
