           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Rick Scott introduces bill to give homeowners tax deduction on insurance premiums</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Sen. Rick Scott (R-Fla.) introduced a bill Wednesday that would provide homeowners a tax deduction on home insurance premiums.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/07/rick-scott-introduces-bill-to-give-homeowners-tax-deduction-on-insurance-premiums/"  >(Kevin Accettulla, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 21:46:18 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 21:46:18 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Zach Schonfeld, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/13/biden-administration-urges-supreme-court-to-reinstate-student-loan-relief-plan-in-emergency-appeal.webp" alt="Biden administration urges Supreme Court to reinstate student loan relief plan in emergency appeal"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Biden administration urges Supreme Court to reinstate student loan relief plan in emergency appeal</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Biden administration filed an emergency appeal Tuesday at the Supreme Court urging the justices to reinstate the president’s latest student loan relief plan.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/13/biden-administration-urges-supreme-court-to-reinstate-student-loan-relief-plan-in-emergency-appeal/"  >(Zach Schonfeld, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:32:46 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:32:46 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/14/kyle-kilbourn-wins-democratic-primary-house-seat-held-gop-rep-tom-tiffany.webp" alt="Kyle Kilbourn wins Democratic primary battle for Wisconsin House seat"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Kyle Kilbourn wins Democratic primary battle for Wisconsin House seat</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Kyle Kilbourn won the Democratic primary to represent Wisconsin&apos;s 7th Congressional District, a seat currently held by Republican Rep. Tom Tiffany.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/14/kyle-kilbourn-wins-democratic-primary-house-seat-held-gop-rep-tom-tiffany/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 02:28:42 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 02:28:42 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MICHAEL HILL and PHILIP MARCELO, Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/13/judge-rules-against-rfk-jr-in-fight-to-be-on-new-yorks-ballot-says-he-is-not-a-state-resident.webp" alt="Judge rules against RFK Jr. in fight to be on New York&#8217;s ballot, says he is not a state resident"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Judge rules against RFK Jr. in fight to be on New York&#8217;s ballot, says he is not a state resident</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      ALBANY, N.Y. (AP) — A judge ruled Monday that independent presidential candidate Robert F. Kennedy Jr.’s name should not appear on New York’s ballot, saying that he falsely claimed a New York residence on nominating petitions despite living in California.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/13/judge-rules-against-rfk-jr-in-fight-to-be-on-new-yorks-ballot-says-he-is-not-a-state-resident/"  >(MICHAEL HILL and PHILIP MARCELO, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 01:29:15 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 01:29:15 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Shannon Bond, Danielle Kurtzleben , and Bobby Allyn, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/13/npr-trump-musk-x-interview.webp" alt="Light on news, heavy on personality in Elon Musk and Donald Trump X interview"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Light on news, heavy on personality in Elon Musk and Donald Trump X interview</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      It was typical Trump fare in an X conversation between the former president and Tesla CEO Elon Musk Monday night. Starting late due to technical issues, the friendly political chat lasted two hours.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/13/npr-trump-musk-x-interview/"  >(Shannon Bond, Danielle Kurtzleben , and Bobby Allyn, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 20:17:29 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 20:17:29 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Nick Robertson, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/12/ocasio-cortez-fires-back-at-vance-over-pro-family-policies.webp" alt="Ocasio-Cortez fires back at Vance over 'pro-family' policies"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ocasio-Cortez fires back at Vance over 'pro-family' policies</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez (D-N.Y.) on Monday fired back at Sen. JD Vance (R-Ohio) after the GOP vice presidential candidate defended his previous attacks on Democrats for being "antifamily." Vance, during appearances on three Sunday morning political shows, was asked about his past criticism.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/12/ocasio-cortez-fires-back-at-vance-over-pro-family-policies/"  >(Nick Robertson, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 13:11:43 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 13:11:43 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Rachel Tucker, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/13/florida-officials-sued-over-states-lab-grown-meat-law.webp" alt="Florida officials sued over state's lab-grown meat law"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Florida officials sued over state's lab-grown meat law</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A company that produces cultivated meat is suing several Florida officials over a new state law that bans their products from being produced or sold in the state.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/13/florida-officials-sued-over-states-lab-grown-meat-law/"  >(Rachel Tucker, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
